\n< Nicola >First, Serena-kun. I want you to take this.

\n< Serena >I was a little curious about where it went,

\n< Nicola >If something like this were to fall into the hands

\n< Serena >What was that just now?

\n< Nicola >I wrote down the circumstances of the fight with
